<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<html class="fontawesome-i2svg-active fontawesome-i2svg-complete">
    <head></head>
    <main class="mb-auto">
      <body>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-xs-9 col-xs-offset-1">
                    <p>ようこそ、ながのCAKEへ！<br>
                    このサイトは、ケーキのECサイトになります。<br>
                    会員でない方も商品の閲覧はできますが、購入には会員登録が必要になります。</p>
                </div>
                
                <h3 class="recommended-items" style="font-family: HiraMinPro-W6; color: #000000;">新着商品</h3>
                <div class="col-xs-9 col-xs-offset-1">
                    <div class="item--card-content">
                        <% @items.each do |item| %>
                            <div class="col-xs-3" style="padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px;">
                                <%= link_to public_item_path(item.id) ,style: "color: black;", data: {"turbolinks" => false} do %>
                                    <%= image_tag item.image, size: '300x200',fallback: "no_image.jpg" %><br>
                                    <%= item.name %><br>
                                    ¥<%= item.price.to_s(:delimited, delimiter: ',') %>
                                <% end %>
                            </div>
                        <% end %>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <p><%= link_to "もっと見る", items_path, class: "pull-right", style: "font-family: HiraMinPro-W6; color: #000000; margin: 30px 0;" %></p>
      </body>
      <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.5.1.slim.min.js" integrity="sha384-DfXdz2htPH0lsSSs5nCTpuj/zy4C+OGpamoFVy38MVBnE+IbbVYUew+OrCXaRkfj" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
      <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/popper.js@1.16.0/dist/umd/popper.min.js" integrity="sha384-Q6E9RHvbIyZFJoft+2mJbHaEWldlvI9IOYy5n3zV9zzTtmI3UksdQRVvoxMfooAo" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
      <script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.0/js/bootstrap.min.js" integrity="sha384-OgVRvuATP1z7JjHLkuOU7Xw704+h835Lr+6QL9UvYjZE3Ipu6Tp75j7Bh/kR0JKI" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    </main>
</html>